data.description: Welcome to Meeker!! Here is your chance for a large home for a GREAT PRICE!! Quiet neighborhood and lovely neighbors!! Meeker Elementary school is not even a block away!  This home has THREE living rooms!! You could use one of the three living rooms as a formal dining space while still having a dining space in the kitchen area. Currently one living space is being used as an office space! This home has a double oven and a wood burning fireplace! The third bedroom you could count as a "mother in law suite". It is a covered attached to home but has been remodeled by current home owners! This mother in law suite has brand new carpet, walls, and a closet!! All vinyl floors throughout, but main living space has some carpet! Garage is a 2 spaced garage but very deep and has a lot of room! 2 covered patios to sit and drink your coffee! Added driveway in front of covered porch! This home has all to offer for a family and is ready for you today!!
